{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"static"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"firstLine"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI17VerticalAlignmentV","text":"VerticalAlignment"}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This alignment is analogous to the default behavior of SwiftUI’s "},{"code":"Label","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", where"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the icon is vertically centered with the first line of the label text. Unlike"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"Label","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", this alignment can be used with any view, any spacing, and any number"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of subviews."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The alignment uses SwiftUI’s text baseline alignment guides to calculate the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"center of the first line. It works by finding the difference between the first"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and last text baselines, then computing the midpoint of the remaining height."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Usage","anchor":"Usage","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use "},{"code":".firstLine","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" as the alignment parameter for "},{"code":"HStack","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":":"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["HStack(alignment: .firstLine, spacing: 12) {","  Image(systemName: \"star.fill\")","    .foregroundStyle(.yellow)","  VStack(alignment: .leading) {","    Text(\"First Line\")","      .font(.headline)","    Text(\"Second Line\")","    Text(\"Third Line\")","  }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The star icon will be vertically centered with “First Line”, regardless of how"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"many additional lines of text appear below."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Common Use Cases","anchor":"Common-Use-Cases","type":"heading"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Timeline entries","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Align node indicators with the first line of event descriptions","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"List items","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Align icons or checkboxes with the first line of multiline labels","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Form fields","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Align validation icons with the first line of error messages","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Comments\/Reviews","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Align avatars with the first line of comment text","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"level":2,"text":"How It Works","anchor":"How-It-Works","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The alignment calculates:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"orderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The height after the first line: ","type":"text"},{"code":"lastTextBaseline - firstTextBaseline","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The height of the first line: ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"totalHeight - heightAfterFirstLine"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The center point: ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"heightOfFirstLine \/ 2"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"inlineCo